10. Abstract This study focuses on the development of guidelines for the close-to- nature river improvement, which enables the improved rivers to show the characteristics of natural rivers. Guidelines for river improvement and computer program for floodwater level estimation were developed. Also, various cases were collected and included for practical applications.
11. Keywords close-to-nature river improvement, design guidelines of close-to-nature revetments, computer program for flood water level estimation
